OL,5, A midwife with long Covid has said she 
OL,6, feels "abandoned and angry".           
OL,8,FNew NHS sickness absence rules mean    
OL,9,FSarah Sutton, 44, from Swansea, will   
OL,10,Fnot be paid after 1 November.          
OL,12,FShe contracted the virus at the start  
OL,13,Fof the pandemic while working as a     
OL,14,Fcommunity midwife at Neath Port Talbot 
OL,15,FHospital.                              
OL,17,FThe Welsh government said NHS Wales and
OL,18,Ftrade unions agreed the new rules for  
OL,19,FCovid sickness absences, which began on
OL,20,F1 July.                                
